TEEsavR23oF.basis.glb_nightstand.lang_desc: nightstand with a teddy bear on it. the nightstand is located to the right of the table lamp and below the bed. the pillow is on the left side of the nightstand, and the plush toy is on the right side of the nightstand.

TEEsavR23oF.basis.glb_picture.lang_desc: picture located in an empty room with a sign on the wall. start by locating the curtain rod towards the top left corner of the view. then, move downwards to find the stairs situated towards the bottom left corner. finally, navigate towards the middle-right section of the view to locate the picture.
the bathroom area. find the picture which shows a bathroom with a sink and mirror. the picture is located near the bath sink and hand soap.
the hallway with a picture of sailboats and an american flag. the picture is located on the left side of the hallway, next to the flag.
picture located to the right of the cabinet, with a curtain above it and a flower below it.

TEEsavR23oF.basis.glb_refrigerator.lang_desc: refrigerator in the kitchen. it is located next to the kitchen cabinet and the worktop.

TEEsavR23oF.basis.glb_microwave.lang_desc: the microwave located in the kitchen cabinet. it is made of stainless steel.

TEEsavR23oF.basis.glb_dresser.lang_desc: the dresser located beside the bed in the room. the dresser has two drawers and a mirror.

TEEsavR23oF.basis.glb_pillow.lang_desc: white pillow near the clothes and iron board.

TEEsavR23oF.basis.glb_mirror.lang_desc: mirror in the bathroom. the mirror is located near the bathroom cabinet and the bath sink. look for it close to the soap bottle and the tap.
